---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Battery Calculators" 
  description="Privacy Policy for the Battery Calculators. We do not track or collect personal data."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12 border-b border-hairline pb-8">
      <span class="text-label-uppercase text-m-blue-light text-xs block mb-4">LEGAL DATA PRIVACY</span>
      <h1 class="text-display-md text-primary mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-body-md text-body font-light">
        Effective date: June 9, 2026.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-body-md text-body font-light">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-lg text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">1. Zero Tracking Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Battery Calculators is a static utility website. We do not use cookies, tracking pixels, or third-party analytics trackers (like Google Analytics). 
        </p>
        <p>
          We do not monitor your searches, inputs, or calculations. All mathematical execution happens completely inside your browser using client-side JavaScript.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-lg text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">2. Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
          This website does not have a database or a backend server. We do not collect or store any system inputs, capacity specs, cable designs, or financial ROI variables. When you refresh the page, all calculations are cleared.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-title-lg text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">3. Hosting</h2>
        <p>
          Our static files are hosted on standard CDNs. The hosting provider may log basic network metadata (like IP addresses and request paths) for security and performance purposes, which is standard for web servers. These logs are not accessible by us and are governed by the hosting provider's security policies.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="border-t border-hairline pt-8">
        <p class="text-body-sm text-muted">
          For any questions about our privacy rules, please review our source files or build configurations directly.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
